'''塔拉山'''（{{lang-sr-Cyrl|Тара}}）是位於[[塞爾維亞|塞爾維亞]]西部的一座山峰，也是第拿里阿爾卑斯山的一部分，海拔高度{{convert|1,000|to|1,590|m|abbr=on}}。塔拉山是一個受歡迎的旅遊目的地，山區的大部分地區位於塔拉山國家公園內<ref name="Politika">{{cite web |url= http://www.politika.rs/sr/clanak/48460/Drustvo/Pluca-Srbije-sve-jaca |author= B.Pejović |title= "Pluća Srbije" sve jača |date= 13 July 2008 |publisher= [[Politika|Politika]] |language= sr |access-date= 2017-12-19 |archive-date= 2019-09-19 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20190919075701/http://www.politika.rs/sr/clanak/48460/Drustvo/Pluca-Srbije-sve-jaca |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref name="nptara">{{cite web |url= http://www.nptara.rs/ |author=  |title= About Tara NP |date= 2013 |publisher= National Park Tara |language=  |access-date= 2017-12-19 |archive-date= 2021-01-26 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210126181612/http://www.nptara.rs/ |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref name="geo">{{cite web |url= http://www.geografija.rs/zasticena-podrucja/zasticena-podrucja-zasticena-podrucja/nacionalni-parkovi/tara/nacionalni-park-tara-proglasenje-i-zone-zastite/ |author=  |title= Nacionalni park Tara – položaj, proglašenje nacionalnog parka i zone zaštite |date= 25 February 2014 |publisher= Geografija.rs |language= sr |access-date= 2017-12-19 |archive-date= 2020-02-16 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20200216155210/http://www.geografija.rs/zasticena-podrucja/zasticena-podrucja-zasticena-podrucja/nacionalni-parkovi/tara/nacionalni-park-tara-proglasenje-i-zone-zastite/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>。
